text.tspan: Share of all cancer deaths by risk factor, United States
Estimated annual share of all cancer deaths attributed to each risk factor .
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2024)

Note: To allow for comparisons between countries and over time, this metric is
age-standardized
. Multiple risk factors can contribute to
the same deaths; therefore, deaths from different risk factors cannot be summed up.
